<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>How to Create Paths to Career Advancement That Matter to Your Employees</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="How to Create Paths to Career Advancement That Matter to Your Employees" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20151130214922-sherpa-nepal-snow-mountain-hike-outdoors-adventure-carrying-weight-back-steps-camping-nature.jpeg" rel="share" />

